import React from 'react'
import { AppBar, Toolbar, Typography, CssBaseline, Link, Button } from '@mui/material'


function Header() {

    return(
    <React.Fragment>
        <CssBaseline />
        <AppBar>
            <Toolbar>
                    <Typography
                        variant="h6"
                        color="inherit"
                        noWrap
                    >
                        <Link
                            to="/"
                            underline="none"
                            color="textPrimary"
                        >
                            Blog
                        </Link>
                    </Typography>
                    <nav>
                        <Link
                            color="textPrimary"
                            href="#"
                            to="/register"
                        >
                            Register
                        </Link>
                    </nav>
                    <Button
                        href="#"
                        color="primary"
                        variant="outlined"
                        to="/login"
                    >
                        Login
                    </Button>
                    <Button
                        href="#"
                        color="primary"
                        variant="outlined"
                        component={NavLink}
                        to="/logout"
                    >
                        Logout
                    </Button>
            </Toolbar>
        </AppBar>
    </React.Fragment>)
}

export default Header
